<td style=" color:#000000; font-size:12pt; background-color:#FFFFFF; font-family:arial; bLabel:main; bEditID:r3st1;" tEditID="c1r1" locked="0" aEditID="c1r1" >
<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><b><span style="line-height: 115%; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: white; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">Please do not
respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and
replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative
on&nbsp;</span><span style="line-height: 115%;">{!Contact.Contact_Owner_alternative_email__c}<o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="line-height: 115%;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Dear {!Contact.FirstName},</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Thank you for completing your application form for a Project Volunteer role on NCS with The Challenge programme.</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">In order for you to volunteer with us we need to undertake certain formalities.</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">All our volunteers must have a valid and approved DBS (Disclosure and Barring Service) to work on the program. Please see below for further instructions &nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>A)<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>I have an enhanced DBS dated after April 30th 2013</b></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please either scan or photograph your whole DBS document and send it to staffing.support@the-challenge.org</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">NB. You will need to take a picture of the whole document and take two close ups - please ensure that that the photographs are as clear as possible.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><b>B)<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>I do not have a DBS (at all or one that is in date)</b></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please start the first part of the application process (see instructions below)</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The instructions for completing a Care Check application are below</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">1.<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Go to www.carecheck.co.uk and click on the Applicant tab</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2.<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Please read all the notes and instructions and click continue to your application.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">3.<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Choose the ‘Disclosure and Barring Service (DBS) Application’ option, and Start Application</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">4.<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Enter the Organisation Reference: evolutionrecruitment</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">5.<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>You do not need a password, press enter to continue with your application</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">6.<span class="Apple-tab-span" style="white-space:pre">	</span>Enter your personal information to apply for the DBS.</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">This is the first step of the DBS application process. The final step is to provide scanned copies of valid ID documents so that we can send your application to the Disclosure and Barring Service. We will ask for these documents shortly.&nbsp;</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">We will be in touch soon. Please contact me if you have any queries!</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Contact.OwnerFullName}</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">e: {!Contact.Contact_Owner_alternative_email__c}</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">The Challenge&nbsp;</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: small; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">CR 1.1b</span></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please Note:-</span></font></p><p class="MsoNormal"><font color="#222222" face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">We employ a third party organisation (Evolution) to carry out our referencing and DBS applications. This process has no bearing on selection and assessment outcomes and is only followed up on post assessment decision. The purpose of starting this process at this stage is to due to a high percentage of successful candidates and the high volume of candidates we need to process.&nbsp;</span></font></p><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div>]]></td>
